Welcome to the Missing Grade Reporting System

This system is designed to help you track and report grades that are not recorded in your academic profiles.

Features:

  • Dashboard: Get an overview of your academic performance and missing grades.
  • Grade Reporting: Easily report grades that are not yet recorded.
  • Missing Grades: Track and manage grades that are currently missing from your profile.
